T02TD1760E:251a-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la bi ta ra s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD1760E:251a-3: dpal mgon po'i nang sgrub ces bya ba /
T02TD1760E:251b-0: dpal nag po chen po la phyag @251b 'tshal lo //
T02TD1760E:251b-2: yid dang mthun pa'i dben gnas su //
T02TD1760E:251b-3: rten dang mchod pa'i rdzas bshams te //
T02TD1760E:251b-4: dang po byang chub sems bskyed la //
T02TD1760E:251b-5: mdun du skad cig 'dab brgyad steng //
T02TD1760E:251b-6: dpal ldan nag po chen po la //
T02TD1760E:251b-7: lha mo brgyad kyis bskor ba yang //
T02TD1760E:251b-8: bya rgod mgo dang khyung gi mgo //
T02TD1760E:251b-9: khva yi gdong dang 'ug pa'i gdong //
T02TD1760E:251b-10: de bzhin phyogs kyi lha mo'o //
T02TD1760E:251b-11: phag gi gdong dang khyi gdong ma //
T02TD1760E:251b-12: spyang ki stag gi gdong can bzhi //
T02TD1760E:251b-13: mtshams kyi lha ni shes par bya //
T02TD1760E:251b-14: kun kyang nag mo gri thod thogs //
T02TD1760E:251b-15: padma ro dang nyi steng na //
T02TD1760E:251b-16: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
T02TD1760E:251b-17: de la bdun po rnam dag gis //
T02TD1760E:251b-18: mchod la gsol ba btab byas la //
T02TD1760E:251b-19: rang bzhin gnas su gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1760E:251b-20: rang nyid yi dam gsal ba'i mdun //
T02TD1760E:251b-21: stong pa'i ngang las pam dang ram //
T02TD1760E:251b-22: padma nyi ma'i steng du h'um //
T02TD1760E:251b-25: sa bon phyag mtshan gyur pa las //
T02TD1760E:251b-26: dpal ldan mgon po'i skur gyur te //
T02TD1760E:251b-27: zhal gcig spyan gsum smin ma 'khyog / khro gnyer zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1760E:251b-28: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du 'bar //
T02TD1760E:251b-29: phyag bzhi g-yas gnyis gri gug dang //
T02TD1760E:251b-31: g-yon gyi phyag gnyis thod khrag dang //
T02TD1760E:251b-32: mdud rtse gsum pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD1760E:251b-33: zhabs gnyis phyed skyil 'gying bag can //
T02TD1760E:251b-34: stag sham mgo phreng ngo shal byas //
T02TD1760E:251b-35: phyag rgya lnga dang ldan pa la //
T02TD1760E:251b-36: klu chen brgyad kyis sku la brgyan //
T02TD1760E:251b-37: de ltar dam tshig gsal bskyed la //
T02TD1760E:251b-38: ye shes spyan drangs mchod cing bstod //
T02TD1760E:251b-39: dza:h'um bam ho:sa dgug gzhug bya //
T02TD1760E:251b-40: sku gsung thugs gsum byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1760E:251b-41: aom badzra ka w'u ba ma h'a k'a la h'um h'um phat /
T02TD1760E:251b-42: man ngag bzhin du bzlas par bya //
T02TD1760E:251b-43: skyon gtor ma phul byas la //
T02TD1760E:251b-44: mchod bstod gsol btab ye shes gshegs //
T02TD1760E:251b-45: dam tshig bsdus la dge ba bsngo //
T02TD1760E:251b-46: dge rtsas bar chad kun bsal nas //
T02TD1760E:251b-47: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par shog / mgon po bya rog gdong can gyi nang sgrub rdzogs so /
T02TD1760E:251b-49: // / pandi ta aa bha y'a ka ra dang /
T02TD1760E:252a-1: ba tsa mi chen pos bsgyur ba'o//
